*   2012: BAM Fisher Block Party with Babycastles, Brooklyn, NY \[[event site](http://www.bam.org/community/2012/bam-fisher-block-party)\]
*   2012: “Joue le Jeu” show at la Gaîté Lyrique, Paris, France \[[exhibition site](http://www.gaite-lyrique.net/theme/joue-le-jeu-ete-2012)\]
*   2012: World Science Festival at NYU-Poly \[[event site](http://worldsciencefestival.com/events/innovation_square)\]
*   2011: Game Set Watch \[[blog site](http://www.gamesetwatch.com/2011/06/ninja_shadow_warrior_photo_boo.php)\]
*   2010 – 2011: X-Lab at Eyebeam Art & Technology Center \[[exhibition site](http://eyebeam.org/events/x-lab)\]

